entry.title: Hexo 常用命令
entry.content: Welcome to Hexo! Quick StartCreate a new post1$ hexo new "My New Post" More info: Writing Run server1$ hexo server More info: Server Generate static files1$ hexo generate More info: Generating Deploy to remote sites1$ hexo deploy More info: Deployment 推荐文章（由hexo文章推荐插件驱动）Hexo的源码保存过程小记
